ON MY Ps AND Qs

29:10.792 --> 29:12.707
WHEN WE WAS OVER IN BOSNIA.

29:12.751 --> 29:14.448
- THAT'S REAL KIND, BUT I
GOTTA TAKE A RAIN CHECK.

29:14.491 --> 29:16.667
TELL LIZ THANKS, THOUGH.
- WAIT A MINUTE.

29:16.711 --> 29:17.973
ARE YOU GOING ON A DATE TONIGHT,YOU SLY DOG?

29:18.017 --> 29:19.801
- NAH, IT'S NOT A DATE.

29:19.845 --> 29:21.063
