EX-HUSBAND THROUGH SCHOOL,

01:05:06.032 --> 01:05:07.904
AND IT WAS PORTABLE,
SO I COULD FIND A JOB

01:05:07.947 --> 01:05:09.035
WHEREVER HIS WORK TOOK HIM.

01:05:09.079 --> 01:05:10.341
- LUCKY MAN.

01:05:10.384 --> 01:05:12.647
- YEAH, EXCEPT NOW I'M RID
OF HIM

01:05:12.691 --> 01:05:14.736
